r66084 | shyouhei | 2018-11-29 11:47:36 +0900 (Thu, 29 Nov 2018) | 5 lines

.travis.yml: fix YAML parse error

`[` is a meta character in YAML.  `- [` starts an array,
so it should end with `]`; but it was not.

