r65798 | shyouhei | 2018-11-19 15:48:09 +0900 (Mon, 19 Nov 2018) | 7 lines

array.c: avoid (VALUE)--

This args[1]-- overflows when it is zero.  Should do that only
when we can say it is nonzero.



