  e.g. The locations of the NODE_SCOPE is fixed:

  ```
  -> x { 1 + 2 }
  ```

  * Before

  ```
  NODE_SCOPE (line: 1, location: (1,2)-(1,14))
  ```

  * After

  ```
  NODE_SCOPE (line: 1, location: (1,3)-(1,14))
  ```
