r64740 | shyouhei | 2018-09-14 17:27:44 +0900 (Fri, 14 Sep 2018) | 6 lines

PRI_64_PREFIX "u" is called PRIu64

See also ISO9899:1999 section 7.8.1 paragraph 3.

The #ifndef is for C compilers older than C99.

