Haven't tested gcc 8, yet; but gcc 6 seems fine....
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r64535 | normal | 2018-08-25 18:02:50 +0900 (Sat, 25 Aug 2018) | 6 lines

hrtime.h: add documentation

