and CLOCK_HIRES seems like it could fail with insufficient permissions:

https://docs.oracle.com/cd/E86824_01/html/E54766/timer-create-3c.html

(Only tested on Linux and FreeBSD)

[ruby-core:88360] [Misc #14937]
