* 2018-04-20
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r63192 | mame | 2018-04-20 00:18:50 +0900 (Fri, 20 Apr 2018) | 7 lines

Introduce endless range [Feature#12912]

Typical usages:
```
p ary[1..]          # drop the first element; identical to ary[1..-1]
(1..).each {|n|...} # iterate forever from 1; identical to 1.step{...}
```
