[DOC] `*` in glob matches `\n` too [ci skip]

```
File.fnmatch("a*b", "a\nb") # => true
/\Aa.*b\z/x.match?("a\nb")  # => false
/\Aa.*b\z/mx.match?("a\nb") # => true
```
