This is required on some platforms to avoid leaks.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r62476 | normal | 2018-02-19 08:58:35 +0900 (Mon, 19 Feb 2018) | 3 lines

thread_pthread.c (thread cache): destroy cond after unlock

