  50: 42
  75: 48
  90: 51
  99: 89
topic:
  50: 49
  75: 55
  90: 58
  99: 99
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r62196 | k0kubun | 2018-02-04 18:48:44 +0900 (Sun, 04 Feb 2018) | 4 lines

Makefile.in: use CFLAGS_NO_ARCH for cpp

Using $(CFLAGS) breaks the build when multiple `-arch` options are
given. Then we should omit arch flags.
