r61620 | svn | 2018-01-06 00:16:43 +0900 (Sat, 06 Jan 2018) | 1 line

* 2018-01-06
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r61619 | mame | 2018-01-06 00:16:42 +0900 (Sat, 06 Jan 2018) | 1 line

node_h (NEW_DEFN): remove unused argument
------------------------------------------------------------------------
