  e.g. The locations of the NODE_ARRAY is fixed:

  ```
  re =~ s1
  ```

  * Before

  ```
  NODE_ARRAY (line: 1, code_range: (1,0)-(1,8))
  ```

  * After

  ```
  NODE_ARRAY (line: 1, code_range: (1,6)-(1,8))
  ```
